E1FCT4A.original: ~z~I got you, bro. I'll be in the area soon.
~z~Don't worry, man. I'll give one of the other boys a call. See you later.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~没关系，哥们。我找其他弟兄问问吧。再见。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey Johnny, it's Terry. Listen, brother, I've got my hands on some guns. Quality shit, real cheap.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~嘿，Johnny，我是Terry。听着兄弟，我手头有些枪，又好又便宜。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Shit Johnny. I can't right now, man. Let's speak later.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~妈的，Johnny，现在没空啊，哥们。晚点再说吧。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Leave it with me. I'll see you soon.
~z~I can't right now, bro I'm drowning in shit. Try me again later.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~我现在没空，兄弟。破事缠身。过后再找我吧。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_REQ_BACKUP_YESA
~z~No can do, brother. Major shit to deal with right now. Call me later and I'll hook you up.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~来不了，兄弟。眼下一堆要紧事情。晚点再找我买家伙吧。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey, it's Terry. They're letting me out of hospital. Can you pick me up?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~嘿，我是Terry。医生叫我出院了。你能来接我吗？

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_REQ_BACKUP_NOA
E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_HILIKEA
~z~Thanks man. See you later.
~z~Sorry Johnny. Tied up right now. I should be free later on.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~不好意思，Johnny。现在忙得很，晚点我才有空。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~There's no way I can get there right now. I'm sorry, Johnny.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~我现在根本来不了。不好意思啊，Johnny。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey Terry, I need your help.
~z~I appreciate it, bro. See you soon.
E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_LOLIKEA
E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_GETCALL_HOSP_NOA
~z~You've had my back and that means a lot to me. So give me a call any time and I'll hook you up.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~平时你很照顾我，对也我够意思。需要枪就打个电话，我会送过来的。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ACCEPTEDA
~z~Sure thing, Johnny. I'll be there as soon as I can.
E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_HILIKEA
~z~Terry. I need your help, brother.
~z~Sorry man. I've got my own shit going down right now.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~抱歉，哥们。我现在有自己的事要忙。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_MEDLIKEA
~z~Sorry, there's no way, Johnny. You know I would if I could, brother.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~对不起，现在没法来啊，Johnny。能来的话我早来了，兄弟。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~No problem, Johnny. I'm on my way.
~z~No problem. I'll be right with you.
~z~No problem, Johnny. I'll be over soon.
E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_YESA
~z~Terry, can you help me out with something?
~z~Sure thing. I'll catch up with you later.
~z~Thanks Terry. That's good to know. I'll be in touch very soon.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~谢了，Terry，真是太好了。有需要我就联系你。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Don't worry, Johnny. I got you.
~z~Sorry, can't right now. Give one of the boys a call.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~不好意思，现在不行。你找其他兄弟吧。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Whatever you say, man. Just thought you might be able to help a brother out.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~你说是就是，哥们。我就来问问你能不能帮兄弟一把。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey Johnny, it's me. I've been released from hospital. Can you give me a ride?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~嘿Johnny，是我啊。我现在出院了。你能来接我吗？

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Johnny man-of-his-word Klebitz. Some fucking friend you are, bro.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~Johnny Klebitz说话算话。真他妈够朋友，兄弟。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey man. I need you to help me out with something.
~z~You've got it, brother. I'll be with you shortly.
~z~Will do. Thanks man.
~z~Yeah, I suppose so. If you're THAT fucking busy.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~好吧，我想也是。如果你丫真那么忙的话。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Yeah, I understand. I got your back but you ain't got mine.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~好，我懂了。我天天支援你，你却不肯帮我。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Can you help me out, bro?
~z~Hey Terry. You still got that hardware?
E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_NOA
~z~I got you covered, Johnny. Hang tight. I'll be there soon.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~包在我身上，Johnny。你等着，我马上到。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Hey man. Can you help me out?
~z~Yeah, do what you've gotta do. It's not like you owe me anything - favors or nothing.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~得了，你该干啥干啥吧。又不是说你欠我人情啥的。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Terry, it's Johnny. I need some hardware. Can you hook me up?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~Terry，我是Johnny。我要弄点家伙。你能整点来吗？

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_MEDLIKEA
~z~I'm tied up right now, man. Can you get one of the boys to pick you up?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~我现在忙得很，哥们。你能叫其他人接你吗？

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_SPECAA
~z~Ahh, sorry man. Can't right now. Give me a shout later.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~啊，不好意思哥们。现在不行。晚点再找我吧。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_CALL_REQ_BACKUPA
~z~Terry. Your services are required, bro. Can we meet up?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~Terry。需要你提供服务，兄弟。能来碰头吗？

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Sure thing, man. I got you. I'll be there in an hour or two.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~可以啊，哥们。我懂了。我一两个小时这样到。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Terry, I need some back-up.
~z~Thanks for nothing, man. I thought we were brothers.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~我谢谢你啊，哥们。亏我还把你当兄弟。

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~Of course, man. I'm on my way.
~z~Hey, it's Johnny. I need some of your merchandise. How soon can you get here?
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~嘿，我是Johnny。我需要来点家伙。你多久能到？

E1FCT4A.original: ~z~No problem, brother. I'll pass by in the next couple hours.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~没问题，兄弟。我过两个小时就到。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ASKA
~z~Anything for a Lost brother.
E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_CALL_REQ_SPECA
~z~Hang tight. I'm on my way.
E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_SPECAB
E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_GETCALL_HOSP_YESA
~z~Listen Terry. I'm not gonna be able to make it to the hospital. Something urgent's come up.
E1FCT4A.translated: ~z~听着Terry。我没法来医院接你了，突然有急事。

E1FCT4A.original: E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_GETCALL_SPEC_THANKSA
E1FCT4_ACT_E1T_CALL_HOSP_CANCELA
~z~I'm in a serious need of some back-up, man.
E1FCT4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_LOLIKEA
